{"tid":253521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講下遇過既柒事","createTime":"2017-05-22T12:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T20:31:47.000Z","uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f9667aae37c3876ef1b6c1ec650b7ef9cdfce3b6","tid":253521,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"以前返學坐巴士<br />\n同男roomate+1個女同學<br />\n咁我就同roomate坐，女同學自己一個座前面<br />\n點知，有個同我地差唔多年紀既毒撚<br />\n主動坐左個女同學格離，之後個毒撚就同佢吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個毒撚我地都唔識，但個女同學又同佢吹水<br />\n吹左10幾分鐘，個毒撚以為得米啦，佢就拎部電話出黎，之後佢就問：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：可唔可以要你電話，日後連絡一下<br />\n<br />\n點知個女同學用一副西口西面既樣答佢：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：吓，我唔想比你wor<br />\n<br />\n哥一刻，雖然我坐係後面，唔關我事<br />\n但我想搵個窿捐入去<br />\n因為真係太柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打後5分鐘我地四個人一言不發<br />\n五分鐘後個毒撚就落左車<br />\n而呢件事都成為左我永久的精神污染<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69dcea92a9c5653f779ad0760fe2833f37d91f59","tid":253521,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T20:07:50.000Z","msg":"有幾柒呀... 咁小事"},{"pid":"7bc5093ee99f50909aebabedfabbccb6b383be50","tid":253521,"uid":111192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T20:31:47.000Z","msg":"幾年前 係康文署體育館既男更衣室換衫  換換下 有個阿叔岩岩沖完涼出黎 赤裸裸咁線左係地下  啪一聲 個阿叔之後若無其事咁起番身"}]}